It is always difficult to put into words a recap for the phenomenal years I get to experience time and time again. Beautiful weddings with clients who trust in me to capture their precious memories. Clients who give me snacks throughout the day when they know I’m nauseous. Clients who text me on my birthday and send holiday cards to our home. Clients who become lifelong friends and send us baby gifts. 
 This job is a weird one. It is challenging and emotional and somedays it takes everything out of me. But it is also extremely rewarding. To know my role helped play a part in someone’s happiness. To know that a photo I took will be hung on the walls of someone’s home for friends and family to view for years to come. To bear witness to beautiful, timeless moments and get to cement them into history. Thank you 2023 couples for making this monumental year an incredibly fulfilling one. 🤍 Love you all and wish you a happy, healthy new year ahead!
